This is the Pedigree native C++ subsystem for user applications. Its purpose is
to provide a C++-style API as an alternative to the C-style POSIX API, as well
as providing a base for future expansion in a Pedigree-specific way.

-- Directory Layout --

./include               <-- Common include files
./kernel                <-- Kernel-side files (specifically, the kernel module)
./user                  <-- User-side files (libpedigree.a)
